title: JavaScript the way that it should have been - JQuery
eventShortDescription: ​Description: John Liu will show you how to use JQuery to add some really fancy and cool client-side functionality to your Web Application. We’ll run through what it is, how to use it, and show as many add-ons as time allows. We can’t promise you will love JavaScript after this session, but we know you will love JQuery!
